885
01:11:27.961 --> 01:11:30.225
Create a leadership team.

886
01:11:32.299 --> 01:11:35.860
Well, if you hope to sell
this leadership team idea,


887
01:11:35.969 --> 01:11:38.164
there's only one way to convince Erich.

888
01:11:38.271 --> 01:11:39.602
And what's that?

889
01:11:39.706 --> 01:11:42.573
