01:12:19.513 --> 01:12:21.481
Dr. Stonehill, please.

896
01:12:22.315 --> 01:12:24.442
Turn it down. Yes.

897
01:12:24.985 --> 01:12:26.816
Yes, the music.

898
01:12:30.090 --> 01:12:31.955
I said down!

899
01:12:33.660 --> 01:12:35.491
This guy's impossible.

