01:12:35.595 --> 01:12:37.392
I like that song.

901
01:12:44.237 --> 01:12:45.397
Hey.

902
01:12:51.244 --> 01:12:53.007
What's up, John?

903
01:12:53.513 --> 01:12:56.539
- Everything all right at home?
- Yeah.


904
01:12:59.719 --> 01:13:02.517
Have you heard that Erich Loring

905
01:13:02.622 --> 01:13:05.921
has agreed to put together
a leadership team?


906
01:13:06.726 --> 01:13:09.024
Yeah, I heard some rumor about it.
What bullshit.


907
01:13:09.129 --> 01:13:14.431
Now I'm gonna have to spend a couple of
hours a week jawin<i>'</i> with Zymagen guys?


908
01:13:15.469 --> 01:13:16.595
No.

909
01:13:16.903 --> 01:13:20.839
No. No, you won't,
'cause I'm not putting you on the team.


910
01:13:21.274 --> 01:13:23.003
What'd you say?

911
01:13:23.276 --> 01:13:25.107
I really wanted to.

912
01:13:25.912 --> 01:13:28.676
You're not putting me on the team?
Is that what you said?


913
01:13:28.782 --> 01:13:31.546
What are you, some varsity track coach?

914
01:13:32.252 --> 01:13:37.690
They didn't buy our company 'cause
