915
01:13:37.924 --> 01:13:39.721
It's me they wanted.

916
01:13:39.826 --> 01:13:43.557
You can't bench me.
It's against the laws of nature.


917
01:13:43.663 --> 01:13:47.690
You're still gonna be able
to prove that your theory is right.


918
01:13:47.801 --> 01:13:52.966
Yeah, but other scientists are gonna
