01:15:00.874 --> 01:15:04.002
Hello? Marcus, hi.

934
01:15:04.911 --> 01:15:06.037
Oh, my God.

935
01:15:06.580 --> 01:15:08.514
Man. I almost got 'em down.

936
01:15:08.648 --> 01:15:11.845
You guys sit tight, okay?
Here, John, grab him.


937
01:15:11.985 --> 01:15:16.115
If there is anything we can do,
anything at all, will you call?


938
01:15:16.656 --> 01:15:19.989
Okay.
We love you guys so much.


939
01:15:21.261 --> 01:15:22.853
Okay, bye-bye.

